eas_text: A CIVIL AUTHORITY HAS ISSUED A REQUIRED MONTHLY TEST FOR THE FOLLOWING COUNTIES/AREAS: Clallam, WA; AT 08:47 PM ON SEP 11, 2025 EFFECTIVE UNTIL 11:47 PM. MESSAGE FROM WSLF/CAP.
extra_text:
This is a test. This is only a test of the Emergency Alert System in Clallam County issued by Clallam County Emergency Management. 

In the event of an emergency, this system would bring you important information. The following tones will conclude this test from Clallam County Emergency Management.
